href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://www.triplepundit.com/2015/02/seafood-distributor-makes-sustainability-policy-front-center/"  data-text="Seafood Distributor Makes Sustainability Policy Front and Center" data-count="horizontal" data-via="triplepundit">Tweet</a></div><div
style="float:left; width:105px;padding-right:10px; margin:4px 4px 4px 4px;height:30px;"><script type="in/share" data-url="http://www.triplepundit.com/2015/02/seafood-distributor-makes-sustainability-policy-front-center/" data-counter="right"></script></div></div><div
style="clear:both"></div><div
style="padding-bottom:4px;"></div><p><img
class="alignright size-medium wp-image-210542" src="http://cdn6.triplepundit.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1158217645_b7181246ff_z-300x225.jpg" alt="seafood" width="300" height="225" />It makes good business sense for a company that sells seafood to buy its products from <a
href="http://www.triplepundit.com/topic/sustainable-seafood-2014/" target="_blank">sustainable</a> sources. <a
href="http://www.sea-delight.com/" target="_blank">Sea Delight</a>, a leading frozen fish distributor, recently made its <a
href="http://sea-delight.com/sustainablepolicy" target="_blank">sustainable seafood policy</a> public &#8212; and front and center &#8212; on its website.</p><p>Sea Delight partnered with <a
href="http://fishwise.org/" target="_blank">FishWise</a>, a sustainable seafood consultancy, to develop the policy. Moving forward, FishWise will collect data on the seafood Sea Delight procures and use the data to assess, monitor and create an evaluation framework.</p><p>Sea Delight has set certain measurable goals for its supply chain, including:</p><ul><li>Increase the overall percentage of <a
href="http://www.sustainablefish.org/fisheries-improvement" target="_blank">fishery improvement projects (FIPs)</a> and/or <a
href="http://www.seafoodwatch.org/" target="_blank">Monterey Bay Aquarium Seafood Watch</a> Green- and Yellow-rated products bought by the company every year.</li><li>Work with one new supplier every year to directly implement FIP activities.</li><li>Create a company traceability policy by the end of 2015.</li></ul> <a
href="http://www.triplepundit.com/2015/02/seafood-distributor-makes-sustainability-policy-front-center/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Seafood Distributor Makes Sustainability Policy Front and Center"> Click to continue reading &raquo;</a><p
class="more"><img
src="http://www.triplepundit.com/wp-content/themes/triplepunditv2/images/page_white_text.png"  alt="Permalink" /> <a
