itemprop="name">4 Trailblazing Green Companies</span></a></h2><div
class="meta"><div
class="authorImg"> <img
alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/247c685dfad19a8d0af7a29cb9eac9dc?s=18&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D18&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-18 photo' height='18' width='18' /></div><div
class="authorInfo"><h5><a
href="http://www.triplepundit.com/writers/" title="Visit 3p Contributor&#8217;s website" rel="author external">3p Contributor</a> |  Thursday February 19th, 2015 | <a
href="http://www.triplepundit.com/2015/02/four-trailblazing-green-companies/#comments" title="Comments on 4 Trailblazing Green Companies"><span
class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="210485 http://www.triplepundit.com/?p=210485">0 Comments</span></a></h5></div></div><div
class="entry"><div
class="bottomcontainerBox" style="border:1px solid #808080;background-color:#F0F4F9;"><div
style="float:left; width:85px;padding-right:10px; margin:4px 4px 4px 4px;height:30px;"> <iframe
src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.triplepundit.com%2F2015%2F02%2Ffour-trailblazing-green-companies%2F&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=85&amp;action=like&amp;font=verdana&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width=85px; height:21px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></div><div
