class="meta"><div
class="authorImg"> <img
alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/456bb52c2e0a8dba085f0e7d5f357076?s=18&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D18&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-18 photo' height='18' width='18' /></div><div
class="authorInfo"><h5><a
href="http://www.triplepundit.com/author/jennifer-boynton/"><span
itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> <span
itemprop="name">Jen Boynton</span></a> |  Wednesday February 18th, 2015 | <a
