style="float:left; width:95px;padding-right:10px; margin:4px 4px 4px 4px;height:30px;"> <a
href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://www.triplepundit.com/2015/02/scheme-things-war-drugs-can-teach-us-keystone-xl/"  data-text="In the Scheme of Things: What the &#8216;War on Drugs&#8217; Can Teach Us About Keystone XL" data-count="horizontal" data-via="triplepundit">Tweet</a></div><div
